{
  "texts": [
    "The reward is zero when the pendulum attends the upright position.",
    "An agent trainer system with Q and Q network learning algorithms is proposed for the data training.",
    "The QL and DQNL control methods return more accurate results in terms of improvement compared to the PID and LQR control methods.The rest of this paper is organized as follows.",
    "In Sect. 2, the dynamic modeling and nonlinear equations of the system are explained.",
    "In Sect. 3, the related principles of RL based on QL and DQNL algorithms for the system control are described."
  ]
}